    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system, both recently serviced to factory tolerances. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission that shifts with bolt-action precision. The suspension geometry remains true, bolstered by fresh bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the variable M differential lock translates every bit of torque to the tarmac. With zero deferred maintenance and a meticulously documented service history, this vehicle offers a pure, high-revving analog experience that is increasingly rare in the current market.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
