      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade example that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, preserved under a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, the original carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. Sale includes all original keys, the complete owner's manual set, and a detailed binder of service records. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
