      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
